_sText:
A fun deathrun map that takes place in the city. Contains 21 pressable traps, and has 49 CT spawns, and 2 T spawns. Testing has already been done so hopefully it's perfect, but if any bugs are discovered feel free to post them and they'll be fixed promptly.

Made for steamgamers.com deathrun server,  66.150.121.71:27015.
